  "comment": "IP Pixelstrip 40 is a high-brightness LED bar with pixel control. Each of the 40 RGB LEDs can be controlled individually by the dedicated Showtec IP Pixel Controller. It has an IP65-rated enclosure with fanless convection cooling, making it suitable for indoor as well as (temporary) outdoor stage applications.\n\nThe short and fixed combined data/power input cable allows the IP Pixelstrip 40 to be daisy-chained and mixed with the IP Pixelstrip 80 up to a total length of 4 metres per controller output. Dedicated cables run from the controller to the IP Pixelstrip for power and data signals (sold separately). A straight alignment plate is included and locks into place without tools. Optional alignment plates allow for more complex configurations, even 3D setups. A standard smoked black flat cover is included and can be easily replaced by an optional white flat cover, white dome-shaped cover or white rectangular cover.\n\nPlease note that stand-alone or direct DMX operation is not possible; the Showtec IP Pixel Controller is required to drive this LED pixel bar.",
